assert (3 == 3 and 3 == 3 and 2 == 3)
 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7205151051c0>([91])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7205151051c0> = [[1, 91], [1, 91, 1], [91], [91, 1], [1, 91], [1, 91, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7205151051c0>([1, 91])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7205151051c0> = [[1, 91], [1, 91, 1], [91], [91, 1], [1, 91], [1, 91, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x7205151051c0>([91, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x7205151051c0> = [[1, 91], [1, 91, 1], [91], [91, 1], [1, 91], [1, 91, 1], ...].count
